reviews.review_text: Goodbye 1989 What a great show! The setlist alone is very impressive and the playing is almost perfect as the Dead say goodbye to the 80's. I almost overlooked this show... glad I didn't. Making the workday go by smoothly.
Phenomenal Show This was the transition into a run of shows through summer tour 90' that were amazing!
GREAT show Builds steadily... Shakedown set 1 closer sets tone for rest of show.
